repair.repairedDockerfile:
# Start from ubuntu
FROM ubuntu:16.04

# Update repos and install dependencies
RUN apt-get update \
  && apt-get -y upgrade \
  && apt-get -y --no-install-recommends install build-essential wget curl libsqlite3-dev zlib1g-dev libpng-dev

# Create a directory and copy in all files
RUN mkdir -p /tmp/tile-count-src
WORKDIR /tmp/tile-count-src
COPY . /tmp/tile-count-src

# Build tile-count
RUN make \
  && make install

# Install tippecanoe since the tests depend on it
ENV TIPPECANOE_VERSION="1.26.3"

RUN wget https://github.com/mapbox/tippecanoe/archive/${TIPPECANOE_VERSION}.tar.gz && \
    tar -xvf ${TIPPECANOE_VERSION}.tar.gz && \
    cd tippecanoe-${TIPPECANOE_VERSION} && \
    make && \
    make install

RUN curl -f https://nodejs.org/dist/v4.8.6/node-v4.8.6-linux-x64.tar.gz | tar zxC /usr/local --strip-components=1

# Run the tests
CMD make test
